Conclusion

  • Males are more likely to be the victim of crimes in Los Angeles

  • The black population is more at risk of becoming victims of crime in Los Angeles

  • Central area has seem consistent increase in Part 1 crimes in the past decade

  • Drug possession arrest in Central area has decreased since 2012

  • Drug possession arrest overall seems to be on a downward trend, potentially related to the new laws passed
